flowchart TD
    QKV["Q, K, V in HBM"]

    QKV -->|"① Read Q, K from HBM"| Compute1["SRAM: Compute S = QKᵀ/√d"]
    Compute1 -->|"② Write N×N matrix to HBM"| S_HBM["S (N×N) stored in HBM\n⚠️ O(N²) memory"]
    S_HBM -->|"③ Read S from HBM"| Compute2["SRAM: Compute P = softmax(S)"]
    Compute2 -->|"④ Write N×N matrix to HBM"| P_HBM["P (N×N) stored in HBM\n⚠️ O(N²) memory"]
    P_HBM -->|"⑤ Read P, V from HBM"| Compute3["SRAM: Compute O = P × V"]
    Compute3 -->|"⑥ Write output to HBM"| Output["Output O in HBM"]

